+# Documentation compatibility markers — 0287-r7-r2-r2
+
+Executable documentation rules treat selected strings as stable public
+traceability anchors. A newer runtime contract therefore must not overwrite the
+baseline version tokens of the cumulative Projects installation guide.
+
+```text
+stable guide baseline: 0287-r5-r1
+stable simplification marker: 0287-r5
+Copilot contract extension: 0287-r7-r2
+active roadmap closure: 0287-r7-r10
+historical Chalouf token: retained but retired
+phase 0288: absent
+```
+
+The correction changes documentation and rule expectations only. It does not
+alter runtime authority, storage, orchestration or remote mutation behavior.
